/* Using Zendesk's Humble Squid template, I found the descriptions associated with Textarea form fields would span the entire width of the form. 
Notice the label "text" in the DIV section below. 
<div class="form-field text  optional  request_custom_fields_xxxxxxxx">
      <label for="request_custom_fields_xxxxxxxx">Preferred Promotion Date details</label>
      <textarea name="request[custom_fields][xxxxxxxx]" id="request_custom_fields_xxxxxxxx"></textarea>
    </div>

The below padding-left causes the textarea descriptions to match the rest of the form.
*/ 


